{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-template-js","path":"/pages/about/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"8d7d747b-8cf1-5ea0-b219-d332d8781fff","html":"<p>Thanks for visiting! My name’s Matthew but I usually go by Matt.</p>\n<p>I am a third-year Mechatronics Engineering student at the University of Waterloo. My occaisional software courses have sparked my interest in aspiring to become a fullstack software engineer. I also love cooking, and reading about history, sociology, and most recently, philosophy.</p>\n<h4 id=\"past-experiences\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#past-experiences\" aria-label=\"past experiences permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Past Experiences</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>In the summer of 2019, I worked as a <em>test developer</em> at <a href=\"https://www.ford.ca/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Ford</a> in Ottawa.</li>\n<li>In early 2020, I got into web development and completed an internship at <a href=\"https://tjene.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Tjene</a>\nas a <em>frontend developer</em>.</li>\n<li>Currently, I’m working as a <em>software engineering intern</em> at <a href=\"https://setter.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Setter</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Not enough info? Here’s <a href=\"/media/resume_f2020.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">a link</a>\nto my resume.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/29635124cd56a5fab0adc019608d02eb/9568a/about_photo.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.75000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/29635124cd56a5fab0adc019608d02eb/8ac56/about_photo.webp 240w,\n/static/29635124cd56a5fab0adc019608d02eb/d3be9/about_photo.webp 480w,\n/static/29635124cd56a5fab0adc019608d02eb/e46b2/about_photo.webp 960w,\n/static/29635124cd56a5fab0adc019608d02eb/f992d/about_photo.webp 1440w,\n/static/29635124cd56a5fab0adc019608d02eb/882b9/about_photo.webp 1920w,\n/static/29635124cd56a5fab0adc019608d02eb/e51ec/about_photo.webp 3024w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/29635124cd56a5fab0adc019608d02eb/09b79/about_photo.jpg 240w,\n/static/29635124cd56a5fab0adc019608d02eb/7cc5e/about_photo.jpg 480w,\n/static/29635124cd56a5fab0adc019608d02eb/6a068/about_photo.jpg 960w,\n/static/29635124cd56a5fab0adc019608d02eb/644c5/about_photo.jpg 1440w,\n/static/29635124cd56a5fab0adc019608d02eb/0f98f/about_photo.jpg 1920w,\n/static/29635124cd56a5fab0adc019608d02eb/9568a/about_photo.jpg 3024w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/29635124cd56a5fab0adc019608d02eb/6a068/about_photo.jpg\"\n          alt=\"Photo of me in Bern, Switzerland a few years ago.\"\n          title=\"Photo of me in Bern, Switzerland a few years ago.\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><em>@ Art Gallery of Ontario. Can’t seem to remember what I was thinking about so profoundly… probably the lack of chairs in the gallery.</em></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"About","date":null,"description":null,"socialImage":{"publicURL":"/static/29635124cd56a5fab0adc019608d02eb/about_photo.jpg"}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/pages/about/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","401334301","825871152"]}